In the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.

Hail and blessed be the hour and moment in which the Son of God was born of the most pure Virgin Mary, at midnight, in Bethlehem, in the piercing cold. In that hour vouchsafe, I beseech Thee, O my God, to hear my prayer and grant my desires, (mention request hereâ€¦) through the merits of Our Savior Jesus Christ, and of His Blessed Mother. Amen. (Note that traditionally this prayer was repeated 15 times per day during Advent.)

In the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.



